  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><br>Enter the world of Laser Tanks, where you must engage in a relentless battle against enemies to succeed in your mission of reviving the Earth. Get involved in a challenging top-down shooter experience. Fight epic battles against alien monsters and rival tanks as you navigate through diverse environments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/29a37dd0cb38ba80a171a0151a073a69.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><br>The year is 2150, and a group of aliens from a mysterious and dangerous world have stolen a crucial semiconductor chip that the entire Earth relies on. The fate of the planet is now in your hands, as you must take on the challenge of restoring it to its former glory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/24875aa6e49b521a691b9c83ee38ce77.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Numerous weapons can be used to knock out alien monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/8f91281bad574d0e120c3f49e2388c75.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Destroy Alien Monsters using various Laser Tanks equipped with powerful Lasers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/b1cd251e070ca9bad48d6ca70bd2459f.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Experience a stunning world of environments like Dark Forests, Dungeons, Sci-Fi, etc.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/21c6836fdee1789909249a11367b020f.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Complete various missions like deactivating CCTVs, unlocking with pin codes, etc.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/afee415285c76785b9bddc796d3f5869.poster.avif?t=1773936683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/afee415285c76785b9bddc796d3f5869.webm?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/afee415285c76785b9bddc796d3f5869.mp4?t=1773936683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309830/extras/4e8247af3cd1fa575ecd8499fee03d57.avif?t=1773936683\" width=616 height=339 /></span><br><br><strong><i> ~ RESTORE EARTH's LIFE ~ </i></strong>",
